  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2584500/extras/5cad630bba459697661b4269ce865ca6.avif?t=1773059782\" width=589 height=101 /></span><br><strong>Surveillance</strong> is a spot the difference horror in which you have to prevent high paranormal activity In different places around the world. Identify suspicious changes in environment and <strong>take immediate action</strong>!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2584500/extras/9c28b103a286d82c64819e0c868a2d7f.avif?t=1773059782\" width=589 height=71 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2584500/extras/8831ca19d70e0488a4ed9e09fc53b03b.poster.avif?t=1773059782\" width=650 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2584500/extras/8831ca19d70e0488a4ed9e09fc53b03b.webm?t=1773059782\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2584500/extras/8831ca19d70e0488a4ed9e09fc53b03b.mp4?t=1773059782\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Many different places require your observation</strong>, includng <strong>Asylum</strong>, <strong>Polar Station</strong>, <strong>Backrooms</strong>, <strong>Spaceship</strong>, and even <strong>Castle</strong>!<br><br><br></li><li>Each location includes several rooms, and you need to keep an eye on each of them!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2584500/extras/0b29a5d37208dd5e7ef97ca42deb05a6.poster.avif?t=1773059782\" width=589 height=71 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2584500/extras/0b29a5d37208dd5e7ef97ca42deb05a6.webm?t=1773059782\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br></li><li>Use advanced <strong>equipment</strong> in your work! EMF detectors, Sound sensors and other technological gadgets are at your disposal!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2584500/extras/af6d5b8b8920d11c0a277fc3ae407a30.poster.avif?t=1773059782\" width=560 height=112 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2584500/extras/af6d5b8b8920d11c0a277fc3ae407a30.webm?t=1773059782\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br></li><li><strong>Upgrade</strong> your devices to get maximum results in your work!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2584500/extras/e8605770d6cd34b76e340c43c2f63280.avif?t=1773059782\" width=589 height=71 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2584500/extras/1c5e1eae20e1e5322cb6df2d91df17a7.poster.avif?t=1773059782\" width=650 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2584500/extras/1c5e1eae20e1e5322cb6df2d91df17a7.webm?t=1773059782\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2584500/extras/1c5e1eae20e1e5322cb6df2d91df17a7.mp4?t=1773059782\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li>You will encounter dozens of different anomalies! Missing objects, strange sounds, intruders from other worlds and much more!<br></li><li>You will never know in advance what awaits you. Anomalies behave <strong>unpredictably</strong> - you can play in same location several times, and each time in a new way!<br></li><li>Beware of <i><strong>especially dangerous anomalies</strong></i>! They pose a serious threat even to a person who is simply <i>watching</i> them on a CCTV monitor.</li></ul><br>",
